{"name":"Canon à concussion","type":"arme","img":"modules/knight-compendium/assets/weapons/canon-concussion.webp","system":{"description":"<p>Ce canon, semblable à un lance-grenades massif doté d'un barillet, propulse à distance des grenades soniques, explosant à l'impact et libérant une superbe onde sonore sur quelques mètres. Comme avec le fusil sonique, l'onde dégagée envoie valser les ennemis dans les airs et a un impact terrible sur les cibles les plus faibles. Le choc de l'explosion de la grenade est généralement si violent que l'environnement proche tremble d'une violente secousse, d'où le nom de « canon à concussion ».</p>\n","rarete":"rare","type":"distance","portee":"moyenne","prix":60,"listes":{},"options2mains":{"has":false,"actuel":"1main","1main":{"degats":{"dice":0,"fixe":0},"violence":{"dice":0,"fixe":0}},"2main":{"degats":{"dice":0,"fixe":0},"violence":{"dice":0,"fixe":0}}},"optionsmunitions":{"has":false,"actuel":"0","value":1,"liste":{}},"tourelle":{"has":false,"attaque":{"dice":0,"fixe":0}},"degats":{"dice":7,"fixe":0},"violence":{"dice":7,"fixe":0},"effets":{"liste":[],"raw":["choc 1","deuxmains","dispersion 6","lourd","obliteration"],"custom":[]},"effets2mains":{"liste":[],"raw":[],"custom":[]},"distance":{"liste":[],"raw":[],"custom":[]},"ornementales":{"liste":[],"raw":[],"custom":[]},"structurelles":{"liste":[],"raw":[],"custom":[]}},"effects":[],"_id":"d3a6b52076292422","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.knight-compendium.weapons-rare.d3a6b52076292422"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"knight","systemVersion":"1.8.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666890009160,"modifiedTime":1668026442564,"lastModifiedBy":"Kisv9JwB5w6zIXyv"}}
{"name":"Lance thermique","type":"arme","img":"systems/knight/assets/icons/arme.svg","system":{"description":"<p>La lance thermique est le croisement conceptuel du trident mâchoire et du stylet thermique. C'est donc une longue lance au fer acéré d'élément alpha. Mais après pénétration, de longues barbelures comme autant de crochets de boucher se déploient d'un coup sec pour hameçonner, immobiliser et diffuser la thermite en combustion à l'intérieur de la cible. Face à une horde, il est possible de maintenir une réaction aluminothermique au bout de la lance en permanence pour l'impact psychologique.</p>\n","rarete":"rare","type":"contact","portee":"contact","prix":90,"listes":{},"options2mains":{"has":false,"actuel":"1main","1main":{"degats":{"dice":0,"fixe":0},"violence":{"dice":0,"fixe":0}},"2main":{"degats":{"dice":0,"fixe":0},"violence":{"dice":0,"fixe":0}}},"optionsmunitions":{"has":false,"actuel":"0","value":1,"liste":{}},"tourelle":{"has":false,"attaque":{"dice":0,"fixe":0}},"degats":{"dice":7,"fixe":0},"violence":{"dice":4,"fixe":0},"effets":{"liste":[],"raw":["antianatheme","degatscontinus 6","deuxmains","lumiere 4","orfevrerie","soumission"],"custom":[]},"effets2mains":{"liste":[],"raw":[],"custom":[]},"distance":{"liste":[],"raw":[],"custom":[]},"ornementales":{"liste":[],"raw":[],"custom":[]},"structurelles":{"liste":[],"raw":[],"custom":[]}},"effects":[],"_id":"fe08ed4014712c3a","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.knight-compendium.weapons-rare.fe08ed4014712c3a"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"knight","systemVersion":"1.8.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666890009162,"modifiedTime":1668026442565,"lastModifiedBy":"Kisv9JwB5w6zIXyv"}}
